1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 6=
=First Kiss on the Beach=

3
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,280
Remember this place?

4
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,600
Why ask?

5
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:18,320
Do you remember who you spent

6
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:19,920
the first money you earned on?

7
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:26,640
Who was it?

8
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:28,920
Can't recall.

9
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,040
Don't tell me you've forgotten the girl

10
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,400
you shared your first kiss with.

11
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,480
I'll count to ten.

12
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:10,380
If you still don't come over,

13
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,040
you're doomed.

14
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,400
Ten.

15
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:17,840
Nine.

16
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,680
Eight.

17
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,920
Seven.

18
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:31,760
Six.

19
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,520
Five.

20
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,440
Four.

21
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,000
Three.

22
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,280
Two.

23
00:02:59,490 --> 00:03:02,500
♪You keep running through my mind♪

24
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,600
One.

25
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,750
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

26
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,310
♪Why?♪

27
00:03:07,650 --> 00:03:11,550
♪You walked out of my world♪

28
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,050
Congrats on getting into college.

29
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,240
A gift for you.

30
00:03:19,660 --> 00:03:24,010
♪Did you hear me say please don't go?♪

31
00:03:25,790 --> 00:03:28,210
♪That song keeps playing on repeat♪

32
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:31,280
♪Feels like
everything has frozen in time♪

33
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,200
Listen.

34
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:37,160
There's the sound of the sea inside.

35
00:03:37,510 --> 00:03:40,380
♪I wonder what you're doing now♪

36
00:03:40,610 --> 00:03:43,540
♪Are you really happier than before?♪

37
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,230
♪Living the life you always wanted♪

38
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:52,090
♪The final note faded away♪

39
00:03:52,090 --> 00:03:54,850
♪Let it be.
Maybe I was just holding on too tight♪

40
00:03:54,850 --> 00:03:57,150
♪Roses are meant to bloom someday♪

41
00:03:57,150 --> 00:04:02,180
♪Look up, you'll see a sky full of stars♪

42
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:05,690
♪You keep running through my mind♪

43
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:08,820
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

44
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,200
♪Why?♪

45
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,800
Ding Daang and Chen Aming

46
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,840
will stay together forever!

47
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,790
♪Can you give me one more hug?♪

48
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,840
That's way too cheesy.

49
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:26,250
♪Did you hear me say please don't go?♪

50
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,240
When you're in class,

51
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,120
try reading less of Rao Xueman's novels.

52
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:32,500
♪I even forgot how small I was♪

53
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:35,440
♪As long as
there's still fire in my heart♪

54
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:38,650
♪I won't let tears blur my eyes♪

55
00:04:38,650 --> 00:04:41,690
♪Silently I pray for you♪

56
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:44,770
♪Wishing you a better life than mine♪

57
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:51,200
♪It no longer matters
if you're not by my side♪

58
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,520
♪The final note faded away♪

59
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:56,320
♪Let it be.
Maybe I was just holding on too tight♪

60
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:58,570
♪Roses are meant to bloom someday♪

61
00:04:58,570 --> 00:05:03,640
♪Look up, you'll see a sky full of stars♪

62
00:05:04,050 --> 00:05:07,170
♪You keep spinning in my mind♪

63
00:05:07,170 --> 00:05:10,210
♪Nothing matters more than you♪

64
00:05:10,510 --> 00:05:11,650
♪Why?♪

65
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:15,880
♪You walked out of my world♪

66
00:05:16,130 --> 00:05:19,100
♪You are my only cure♪

67
00:05:19,100 --> 00:05:22,210
♪Can you give me one more hug?♪

68
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:28,090
♪Did you hear me say please don't go♪

69
00:05:28,090 --> 00:05:31,040
♪My world once shined because of you♪

70
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:33,890
♪I even forgot how small I was♪

71
00:05:34,090 --> 00:05:36,910
♪As long as
there's still fire in my heart♪

72
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:39,970
♪I won't let tears blur my eyes♪

73
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:42,840
♪Silently I pray for you♪

74
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:46,190
♪Wishing you a better life than mine♪

75
00:05:47,870 --> 00:05:53,230
♪It no longer matters
if you're not by my side♪

76
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,200
Why are you staring at me like that?

77
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,320
Give me a hand.

78
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:01,880
These hands of mine

79
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:04,480
are only good for typing code,

80
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:06,040
not for manual labor like this.

81
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,600
Stop being so cheeky.

82
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,320
Help me peel these chestnuts.

83
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:32,320
When did you get so slick?

84
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,280
Yes, ma'am.

85
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,600
This one's rotten.

86
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,240
This one's rotten too.

87
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,800
And this one too.

88
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,440
This one as well.

89
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,190
Trying to sneak up on me?

90
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,960
That's what you get for that.

91
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,080
Is it sweet?

92
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,200
Not sweet enough.

93
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,440
Now that's much better.

94
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,200
(Aming)

95
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:46,480
(If time could freeze right now,)

96
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,960
(that'd be perfect.)

97
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,800
What are you doing?

98
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,220
The love guru gave it to me.

99
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,720
He said my old deck was too worn out.

100
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,800
Sis.

101
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,960
That girl from yesterday...

102
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,960
The one with short hair.

103
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,520
Is she your coworker?

104
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,640
Yeah.

105
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,440
What's her name?

106
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,520
Lin Xibei.

107
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,240
Wow,

108
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,800
you finally warmed up to someone.

109
00:08:16,640 --> 00:08:18,400
Go for it, I'm rooting for you.

110
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,880
She doesn't talk much though.

111
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,640
Even less than you.

112
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,240
Gu Ruofei,

113
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,320
delete all my info from your phone.

114
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,840
Right now. Immediately.

115
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,600
I don't use a phone.

116
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:33,600
Also,

117
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,080
how do you even know my name?

118
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,040
Ding Daang.

119
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,920
When did you buy them?

120
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,880
I passed a little shop earlier.

121
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:04,040
Thought they would suit you.

122
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,880
So I bought them.

123
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,960
Chen Aming.

124
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,120
When did you learn to lie?

125
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,400
Don't think I don't know
how much they cost

126
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:14,000
just because you took the packaging off.

127
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,080
You've got no sense of fun at all.

128
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,920
Do you like it?

129
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:21,920
It's okay, I guess.

130
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,320
Let me put them on you.

131
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,040
I can do it myself.

132
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,440
Sure you don't need my help?

133
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:33,800
The kitchen's over there.

134
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:36,400
And the oven's next to the fridge.

135
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,920
Cabinet under the oven holds...

136
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:38,800
I remember it all.

137
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,880
Back then,

138
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:42,160
my mom was taking care of you.

139
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:44,250
She barely had time for me and Miaomiao.

140
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,680
Your dad let me drop by to grab dinner.

141
00:09:47,770 --> 00:09:49,600
I got plenty of dirty looks
from your stepmom.

142
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,400
Put your feet down.

143
00:09:51,400 --> 00:09:52,920
Look at you, what do you look like?

144
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,320
You came in third to last

145
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,040
in the whole grade on the finals.

146
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,560
Even my teacher came knocking.

147
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:01,840
Don't you have any shame?

148
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,440
Liu Xiaoting.

149
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,600
Stop acting like you own the place.

150
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,680
This is the Ding household.

151
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:09,400
The Ding household is my home.

152
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,260
Wait till your dad gets back
to deal with you.

153
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:20,000
Stop bossing me around here.

154
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:22,040
You cozied up to my dad's bed

155
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:23,680
just to get inside like a parasite.

156
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,680
Why don't you get lost.

157
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,560
You've got zero manners.

158
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,880
I bet you'll shame the Ding family
sooner or later.

159
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,160
None of your business.

160
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,480
A home full of parasites.

161
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,480
Those earrings are worth
nearly a hundred grand.

162
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,920
Let me tell you something.

163
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,560
Where a man's money is,

164
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:54,800
his heart usually follows.

165
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,440
I'm not after his money.

166
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,840
Then you better be careful.

167
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,680
Who knows,

168
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:01,360
maybe he's after yours.

169
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,760
And if he is?

170
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,200
So what?

171
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:05,760
How about this:

172
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:07,840
You've got nine love-struck brains.

173
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,960
Can I borrow one?

174
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,440
What's up?

175
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,400
Got something going on?

176
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,440
I'm still weighing things up.

177
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:15,300
I'll let you know if anything comes up.

178
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:16,560
Alright then.

179
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,880
Tell me if something happens.

180
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:19,760
No matter what happens,

181
00:11:19,760 --> 00:11:21,200
don't forget what we came for.

182
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:22,160
Stay safe out there.

183
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:23,200
Got it.

184
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,920
Speaking of Miaomiao,

185
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,080
she should be about...

186
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,600
twenty now, right?

187
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:42,880
I haven't really

188
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,200
seen her much.

189
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,040
Aming!

190
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,840
Come back!

191
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,000
I don't want to waste my time.

192
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,280
I'm sorry.

193
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,780
Everyone I've ever loved

194
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:56,880
ends up leaving me.

195
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,320
But I'm not afraid.

196
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,840
This wedding is not gonna happen.

197
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,840
If everything in the past was a lie,

198
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:07,040
then end me.

199
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:07,880
But I'm scared.

200
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,200
I used to be scared.

201
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,640
Now I'm still scared.

202
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,600
Chen Aming.

203
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,040
Still can't let it go?

204
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,400
You really think you can get out?

205
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:50,040
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

206
00:12:54,440 --> 00:13:01,800
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

207
00:13:06,250 --> 00:13:08,190
♪They say♪

208
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:16,980
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

209
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:20,480
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

210
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:26,650
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

211
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:33,790
♪I've already lost you♪

212
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:39,270
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

213
00:13:39,570 --> 00:13:45,520
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

214
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:50,300
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

215
00:13:51,410 --> 00:13:55,440
♪The past will always pass♪

216
00:13:55,770 --> 00:14:03,350
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

217
00:14:03,820 --> 00:14:07,070
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

218
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:13,280
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

219
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:19,270
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

220
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:25,530
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
